<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px;">
  <h2 style="color: #dc3545;">⚠️ CAB Approval Required</h2>
  
  <div style="background: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #dc3545; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
